OL,3,CTwo young people arrested after fire
OL,4,Cat derelict development
OL,6,FTwo young people have been arrested in
OL,7,FGuernsey following a fire at Leale's
OL,8,FYard.
OL,10,FGuernsey Fire and Rescue Service
OL,11,Fattended the scene after it was
OL,12,Freported just after 17:00 today. It
OL,13,Fwas then put out by fire crews by
OL,14,F18:30.
OL,16,FPolice are appealing for witnesses to
OL,17,Fcome forward.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
