OL,3,CTwo young people arrested after fire
OL,4,Cat derelict development
OL,6,FA statement from Guernsey Police
OL,7,Freads: "This evening Guernsey Police
OL,8,Fhas arrested two young people on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of arson in relation to the
OL,10,Ffire at Leale's Yard this afternoon.
OL,12,F"Enquiries are now ongoing and we'd
OL,13,Fask that anyone with any information,
OL,14,For who may have seen what happened, to
OL,15,Fcontact officers on 01481 222 222."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
